{"tid":763903,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[代糖撚]有無糖尿病人仕知道邊度有好既甜菊糖賣?","createTime":"2018-08-01T13:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T14:57:35.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84b9f571c34aa29d87a9501c6cc44e5d113bf600","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"係惠康買左太古隻甜菊糖 完全搵笨柒 <br />\n上網睇甜菊糖甜度係砂糖既200-300倍 <br />\n但落太古隻甜菊糖 屌 仲要落多過砂糖一倍先夠甜<br />\n之後睇返個label<br />\n100g 入面有成99.5g都係甜度只係砂糖60-70%既赤蘚糖醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頂盡都只係得0.5g甜菊糖苷<br />\n一包只得150g仲要賣成36蚊包 甜菊糖苷仲要溝到咁撚淡 屌佢老味<br />\n<br />\n我知赤蘚糖醇係用黎溝淡甜菊糖既苦味 <br />\n我睇外國隻Truvia, 3.5g入面只有3g係赤蘚糖醇<br />\n人地寫到明3/4 teaspoon provides the same sweetness as 2 teaspoons of sugar <br />\n甜菊糖苷含量一定高D 無咁搵笨<br />\n<br />\n但香港有無高甜菊糖苷含量既甜菊糖賣?<br />\n邊度有得賣? 度度都搵唔到 黎黎去去都係太古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978e8cd5b72d47c13f13af82bc43dacd1158a062","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"028226e6d9afa123f4c6b698920faca5eebea844","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fca007dcf36666c0b4e77f6203f19703ab6f2b0","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fddb2ece28e28f3a8ac87c9b101d8db5769c77a","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n見到iherb 有隻叫sweetleaf <br />\n佢又分好多種 又extract又solution<br />\n有貴有平 有無巴打試過邊隻好?"},{"pid":"3faaa5c290214712f350117824d0b8c9cd111343","tid":763903,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"呢度無人食代糖?"}]}